::Zardus/DeathStorm/Shredder/Zenyak/Mosquitor::

Zardus walks up behind Wolfgang. "About time you got back."

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

DeathStorm lands outside his ship. The ship's comp had located several maximal signitures nearby. He walks inside to get a quick dip in a CR chamber.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Shredder grunts under the speeder's weight. He didn't like this at all. He walks on quietly.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Zenyak exits the CR chamber and walks to the bridge. He looks around at Hell Beast and the rest of the predacons.

"Next time I see Shredder, he dies." He mumbles to himself as he sits down at a comp console.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Mosquitor walks into the bridge. He had been repaired in a CR chamber from his little encounter with Ominous and Transantulus.

"It is good that we have finally taken back the ship, Leadership."
